It is a linear data structure and it is abstract data type
we can access the data only sequencialy and randomly like array
the main advantage of using liked list is that it is dynamic and easily add and erase data with out any memory related problems
types of linked list;
1-> singly 
2-> doubly
3-> circular (optional)(same like double extra thing is last->next = head)

lined list is basic for queue, stack , tree and all other concept implementation

